{"tid":1216601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「全城怒睥黑警」行動","createTime":"2019-06-13T10:28:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T14:05:36.000Z","uid":165200,"like":249,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"6d3bd83f2f2e1f77f6c4f78c6bace57be3fac939","tid":1216601,"uid":165200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:28:35.000Z","msg":"自69、612兩日後，各式和理非非、激進、以武止暴，以至不合作運動等等招數都有人出過。小弟不才，一直喺連登都只係個有account嘅cdrom，從未出post。但今誠香港危急存亡之秋，都想出一分力，諗吓有乜最低成本嘅抗爭手法。<br />\n<br />\n終於，今朝出門時，喺樓下見到幾個工賊會嘅仆街派傳單，心中忽生一計，非常簡單，人人都可參與，完全合法，成本低無可低：<br />\n<br />\n1. 「攻擊」對象：主要係黑警，其次所有建制賊都係追擊目標<br />\n2. 方法：易到極，每次見到目標人物，只需當佢哋殺父仇人咁，怒睥佢哋！<br />\n<br />\n今早試咗一次，個工賊義工本來四萬咁口遞張傳單畀我，我一睥，即時睇住佢個心離一離 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，成個人後退幾步，真係幾箋鬼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（記住忍笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n試想像一下，如果參與人數夠多，除有表態作用，呢班賣港賊每日行出街就會覺得被人十面埋伏，好似過街老鼠咁，大大增加佢哋心理壓力。<br />\n<br />\n而我哋成本？幾乎係零！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好睇小心理戰，只要影響到5%黑警，負面情緒好易骨牌式擴散，隨時有機會令開心浩園餐賣斷市 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e50372d59713e24b9631c7518bdaac84f52e9d","tid":1216601,"uid":108016,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:30:06.000Z","msg":"星期日帶定箱雞蛋去<br />\n請警犬食"},{"pid":"1c0b32abcff9e85b3e53fb9c3893d8db70c69d3d","tid":1216601,"uid":149607,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:30:08.000Z","msg":"全城帶頭盔口罩行動點睇?"},{"pid":"afceadf0c5c482243ba8b4a60c03e6749bb05ac4","tid":1216601,"uid":29702,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:30:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d851ecb3df2b87310982cdbc0b6105256c5aed5f","tid":1216601,"uid":81518,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:33:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"361703b3f0d6e036c8ea9ecac34d7bee81a6b54d","tid":1216601,"uid":45934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:36:05.000Z","msg":"其實電梯眼打量更加好"},{"pid":"2591973682a24b5764f9588380d837ec6493f17e","tid":1216601,"uid":74954,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"77e50372d59713e24b9631c7518bdaac84f52e9d","tid":1216601,"uid":108016,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:30:06.000Z","msg":"星期日帶定箱雞蛋去<br />\n請警犬食"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:36:19.000Z","msg":"喂喂喂  你講野小心d <br />\n我地市民唔洗食?  我就買定蕃茄 大家可以補充體力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ec25fc5899a29fc828bef78a897fd78223faec","tid":1216601,"uid":7790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:37:10.000Z","msg":"全城屌狗行動<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d66b060e4d1205570c986174aa3ff5cad4f3164","tid":1216601,"uid":165200,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"afceadf0c5c482243ba8b4a60c03e6749bb05ac4","tid":1216601,"uid":29702,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:30:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:38:53.000Z","msg":"唔洗分邊個方法「有用啲」，只要有作用，你又做得到嘅，可以全部做哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b76d5cb0a47a941d376f2b83b9eed809a429b107","tid":1216601,"uid":13117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:45:07.000Z","msg":"呢啲好啊，係要多啲呢種唔犯法既行動"},{"pid":"88ac8ef9c72f166ff264973e6209629858937175","tid":1216601,"uid":114483,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e442b9b2042c8c0b9c14c3